sudo snap install maltego
Issue 2: Transform Failures
Problem: Maltego transforms fail to execute

Solution:

Check internet connectivity
Verify API keys if using premium transforms
Try running transforms individually
Check Maltego logs in View > Show Messages
Issue 3: Tool Integration Issues
Problem: External OSINT tools not working with Maltego

Solution:

# Verify tool installations
which theharvester
which dnsrecon
which python3

# Check Python dependencies
pip3 list | grep -E "(requests|beautifulsoup4|dnspython)"

# Reinstall problematic tools
sudo apt remove theharvester
sudo apt install theharvester
Issue 4: Memory and Performance Issues
Problem: Maltego becomes slow with large graphs

Solution:

Increase Java heap size in Maltego settings
Use graph filtering to show only relevant entities
Break large investigations into smaller focused graphs
Regular save your work to prevent data loss
